com.appdynamics.instrumentation.sdk.contexts

Interface ISDKUserContext


  • public interface ISDKUserContext
    This interface represents the API for a context available to consumers of the Instrumentation SDK. This context will be passed as an argument to each method implemented by the user. Objects can be stashed during any method, and will be available for fetching in any subsequent method. This context will be cleared af the completion of every individual invocation of a transaction. Created by ryan.terbush on 3/25/16.
